     *----------------------------------------------------------------
     *  Let the show begin .....
     *
     C     *entry        plist
     C                   parm                    $parms
     *----------------------------------------------------------------
     *  Main line
     *
     C                   eval      *in97 = *on
     C                   eval      *in90 = *off
     C                   eval      *in91 = *off
     C                   eval      error = *off
     C                   eval      $prtn = *blanks
     C                   eval      $perm = *blanks
     *
     C                   exsr      zzinz2
     C                   if        error = '1'
     C                   eval      nxtscr = 'EOJ'
     C                   endif
     *
     C                   dow       nxtscr <> 'EOJ'
     C                   exsr      dspscr
     C     nxtscr        caseq     '01 '         sc1
     C                   endcs
     C                   enddo
     *
     *   Do some clean up before leaving.
     *
     C                   exsr      zsclr
     C                   return
