     C                   endif
     *
     *   Overlay screen with error messages
     *
     C                   exsr      zmdmsg
     *
     *  Overlay screen with screen to be processed.
     *
     C                   if        nxtscr = '01 '
     C                   exfmt     screen1                              50
     C                   endif
     *
     *   Initialize error indicators and fields
     *
     C                   setoff                                       010203
     C                   setoff                                       040506
     C                   setoff                                       070809
     C                   setoff                                       101112
     C                   setoff                                       131415
     C                   setoff                                       161718
     C                   setoff                                       1920
     C                   setoff                                       212223
     C                   setoff                                       242526
     C                   setoff                                       272829
     C                   setoff                                       303132
     C                   setoff                                       333435
     C                   setoff                                       363738
     C                   setoff                                       3940
     C                   setoff                                       98
     C                   eval      warn = *off
     C                   eval      error = *off
     C                   eval      cmdtkn = *off
